# vocino.com — project baseline

Full detail: [CLAUDE.md](../../CLAUDE.md). README may still mention Jekyll; this repo is **Astro + Cloudflare Pages (SSR)**.

## Commands

- Dev: `npm run dev` / `npm start`
- Build (includes typecheck): `npm run build`
- Preview: `npm run preview`
- Types only: `astro check`

## Must follow

- **SSR** via `@astrojs/cloudflare`; site URL https://vocino.com
- **Single page**: only `src/pages/index.astro` is public; `/bg3` redirects to `/`
- **Pages** use `BaseLayout` from `src/layouts/BaseLayout.astro` — inherit dot grid, scanlines, fonts, SEO
- **API** in `src/pages/api/` only — not Cloudflare Pages Functions
- **Cloudflare env** in production: `locals.runtime.env` (not `process.env`); use `runtime.waitUntil()` for background cache writes
- **SCSS** imported in layouts (`import '../styles/main.scss'`), not `<link>` tags; tokens in `_variables.scss`
- **TypeScript** strict mode; run `npm run build` after substantive edits
- **Commits**: only when the user explicitly asks
